name: Obi-Wan's Apparition (V)
Lore: '''Luminous beings are we, not this crude matter.'' The inner consciousness of a Jedi can transcend even death.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. May place your just lost Jedi out of play. May use X Force to add X to a just drawn weapon or battle destiny, where X = number of your Jedi out of play.',
